<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>VidyaKul Education Hub</title>
    <!-- Google Fonts for professional look -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&family=Yatra+One&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- FontAwesome for Icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-dark: #0f2a24;
            --accent-gold: #d4af37;
            --text-light: #ffffff;
            --text-dark: #333333;
            --bg-light: #f4f7f6;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-light);
            color: var(--text-dark);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Hero Section mimicking the banner vibe */
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(15, 42, 36, 0.85), rgba(15, 42, 36, 0.95)), 
                        url('170655.jpg') no-repeat center center/cover;
            color: var(--text-light);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px 20px;
            border-bottom: 5px solid var(--accent-gold);
        }

        .tagline {
            font-family: 'Yatra One', cursive, sans-serif;
            color: var(--accent-gold);
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }

        .cta-btn {
            background-color: var(--accent-gold);
            color: var(--primary-dark);
            padding: 12px 30px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .cta-btn:hover {
            background-color: var(--text-light);
            color: var(--primary-dark);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        /* Course Structure Section */
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 60px 20px;
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            color: var(--primary-dark);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .section-title::after {
            content: '';
            display: block;
            width: 80px;
            height: 4px;
            background-color: var(--accent-gold);
            margin: 10px auto 0;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .course-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            border-top: 5px solid var(--primary-dark);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .course-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            border-top-color: var(--accent-gold);
        }

        .icon-box {
            background: rgba(15, 42, 36, 0.1);
            color: var(--primary-dark);
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .lang-block {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .lang-block:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
            padding-top: 15px;
            border-top: 1px dashed #e0e0e0;
        }

        .eng-title, .hin-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            color: var(--primary-dark);
        }

        .eng-desc, .hin-desc {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #666;
        }

        /* Footer & Contact details */
        footer {
            background-color: var(--primary-dark);
            color: var(--text-light);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .contact-info {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 40px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .contact-info a {
            color: var(--text-light);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .contact-info a:hover {
            color: var(--accent-gold);
        }

        .contact-info i {
            color: var(--accent-gold);
            margin-right: 8px;
        }

        .web-link {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--accent-gold);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* Responsive Settings */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .tagline { font-size: 1.8rem; }
            h1 { font-size: 2.3rem; }
            .contact-info { flex-direction: column; gap: 15px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Hero Header Background Front Image -->
    <header>
        <div class="tagline">सपनों को उड़ान दें!</div>
        <h1>VidyaKul Education Hub</h1>
        <p>Empowering minds from schooling up to higher research preparation.</p>
        <a href="tel:+917479925807" class="cta-btn"><i class="fa fa-phone"></i> Call Now to Enroll</a>
    </header>

    <!-- Academic Offerings -->
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Our Programs / हमारे पाठ्यक्रम</h2>
        
        <div class="grid">
            <!-- 1. Schooling -->
            <div class="course-card">
                <div class="icon-box"><i class="fa-solid fa-graduation-cap"></i></div>
                <div class="lang-block">
                    <div class="eng-title">Schooling (Class 1-7)</div>
                    <div class="eng-desc">CBSE, BSEB & Others</div>
                </div>
                <div class="lang-block">
                    <div class="hin-title">स्कूली शिक्षा (कक्षा 1-7)</div>
                    <div class="hin-desc">CBSE, BSEB एवं अन्य बोर्ड</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 2. 10+2 -->
            <div class="course-card">
                <div class="icon-box"><i class="fa-solid fa-scale-balanced"></i></div>
                <div class="lang-block">
                    <div class="eng-title">10+2 / Senior Secondary</div>
                    <div class="eng-desc">All Boards</div>
                </div>
                <div class="lang-block">
                    <div class="hin-title">10+2 / इंटरमीडिएट</div>
                    <div class="hin-desc">सभी बोर्ड</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 3. UG -->
            <div class="course-card">
                <div class="icon-box"><i class="fa-solid fa-brain"></i></div>
                <div class="lang-block">
                    <div class="eng-title">Undergraduate (UG)</div>
                    <div class="eng-desc">B.A. / B.Sc.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="lang-block">
                    <div class="hin-title">स्नातक (UG)</div>
                    <div class="hin-desc">B.A. / B.Sc.</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 4. M.A History/PolSci -->
            <div class="course-card">
                <div class="icon-box"><i class="fa-solid fa-user-astronaut"></i></div>
                <div class="lang-block">
                    <div class="eng-title">Postgraduate M.A.</div>
                    <div class="eng-desc">Ancient & Modern History, Political Science</div>
                </div>
                <div class="lang-block">
                    <div class="hin-title">एम.ए (M.A)</div>
                    <div class="hin-desc">इतिहास (प्राचीन/आधुनिक), राजनीति विज्ञान</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 5. M.A Psychology -->
            <div class="course-card">
                <div class="icon-box"><i class="fa-solid fa-lightbulb"></i></div>
                <div class="lang-block">
                    <div class="eng-title">M.A. Psychology</div>
                    <div class="eng-desc">Psychology Honors & Ph.D. Preparation</div>
                </div>
                <div class="lang-block">
                    <div class="hin-title">एम.ए मनोविज्ञान</div>
                    <div class="hin-desc">मनोविज्ञान ऑनर्स एवं पीएचडी प्रवेश परीक्षा तैयारी</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 6. M.Sc Biology -->
            <div class="course-card">
                <div class="icon-box"><i class="fa-solid fa-dna"></i></div>
                <div class="lang-block">
                    <div class="eng-title">Postgraduate M.Sc.</div>
                    <div class="eng-desc">Biology, Botany & Zoology</div>
                </div>
                <div class="lang-block">
                    <div class="hin-title">एम.एससी (M.Sc)</div>
                    <div class="hin-desc">जीव विज्ञान, वनस्पति विज्ञान, प्राणी विज्ञान</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Contact Footer bar identical to poster baseline info -->
    <footer>
        <div class="contact-info">
            <a href="tel:+917479925807"><i class="fa fa-phone"></i> +91 74799 25807</a>
            <a href="tel:+919771160889"><i class="fa fa-phone"></i> +91 97711 60889</a>
        </div>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Visit our official portal:</p>
        <a href="http://www.vidyakuleducation.com" class="web-link" target="_blank">www.vidyakuleducation.com</a>
        <p style="margin-top: 25px; font-size: 0.85rem; opacity: 0.6;">&copy; 2026 VidyaKul Education Hub. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
